    "description": "<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813230/extras/a7a934d6dca254c82bbf26f634a7379f.poster.avif?t=1744072617\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813230/extras/a7a934d6dca254c82bbf26f634a7379f.webm?t=1744072617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813230/extras/a7a934d6dca254c82bbf26f634a7379f.mp4?t=1744072617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Build your own Wild West town from scratch! Create a dream city for cowboys and cowgirls. It is totally up to you how it will look and prosper.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813230/extras/293f9c6993d907116347c9330df72590.poster.avif?t=1744072617\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813230/extras/293f9c6993d907116347c9330df72590.webm?t=1744072617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813230/extras/293f9c6993d907116347c9330df72590.mp4?t=1744072617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Gather resources in order to expand. There are many different structures to choose from- saloon, general store, gunsmith, church, stables, hotel, post office and many more! You can focus on upgrading your existing town or move on to the next one when you're ready.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813230/extras/574455a0f27646f92809643a5823bac5.poster.avif?t=1744072617\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813230/extras/574455a0f27646f92809643a5823bac5.webm?t=1744072617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813230/extras/574455a0f27646f92809643a5823bac5.mp4?t=1744072617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Protect your citizens! There will be folks who will try to disturb your peace. You'll need to keep your eyes open at all time. Hire the sheriff, the hangman and let them do their job...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813230/extras/93e1c15d0b3f6dc8497c358af3a01c28.poster.avif?t=1744072617\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813230/extras/93e1c15d0b3f6dc8497c358af3a01c28.webm?t=1744072617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1813230/extras/93e1c15d0b3f6dc8497c358af3a01c28.mp4?t=1744072617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore the desert and find new places to live. Build the railway station and expand the railroad network between your cities- that way you can move materials and citizens between them!",
